      "rationale": "In-vitro hemolysis tests conducted at ASTM F1841 conditions with bovine blood (hematocrit 33±1%). Five operating points span the CPB envelope. Temperature, anticoagulation protocol, and loop priming volume documented. Test conditions map directly to CFD boundary conditions."
